Rowberg 00 (Richard E., Senior Specialist in Science and Technology in the Resources, Science, and Industry Division – CRS, &amp;#34;Congress and the Fusion Energy Sciences Program: A Historical Analysis&amp;#34;, Congressional Research Service Report, 1-31, http://fire.pppl.gov/RL30417.pdf)&#xD;
