Fission incentives now&#xD;
Goodman 12 (Amy, Award Winning Journalist – The Guardian and Host – Democracy Now%21, &amp;#34;Big Nuclear~’s Cosy Relationship with the Obama Administration&amp;#34;, The Guardian, 3-8, [[http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/-http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/]] cifamerica/2012/mar/08/big-nuclear-cosy-relationship-obama-administration)&#xD;
