**Makhijani 98** (Arjun, President – Institute for Energy and Environmental Research, &amp;#34;Statement Before the National Press Club&amp;#34;, 7-15, http://ieer.org/wp/wp-content/uploads/1998/07/dtq-statement-arjun.pdf)&#xD;
