</headline></objectSummary><objectSummary><link rel="http://www.xwiki.org/rel/object" href="http://opencaselist.paperlessdebate.com/xwiki/rest/wikis/opencaselist/spaces/Michigan%20State/pages/Butler-Caporal%20Aff/objects/Admin.EntryClass/50"/><link rel="http://www.xwiki.org/rel/properties" href="http://opencaselist.paperlessdebate.com/xwiki/rest/wikis/opencaselist/spaces/Michigan%20State/pages/Butler-Caporal%20Aff/objects/Admin.EntryClass/50/properties"/><id>opencaselist:Michigan State.Butler-Caporal Aff:c722dfb6-8328-499a-a0f6-3f478f0240b0</id><guid>c722dfb6-8328-499a-a0f6-3f478f0240b0</guid><pageId>opencaselist:Michigan State.Butler-Caporal Aff</pageId><wiki>opencaselist</wiki><space>Michigan State</space><pageName>Butler-Caporal Aff</pageName><className>Admin.EntryClass</className><number>50</number><headline>==*** 1AC vs mich==&#xD;
