Pure fusion weapons have long been a dream for nuclear weapons designers. Present-&#xD;
AND&#xD;
relatively small pure fusion weapons would be much larger than today~’s nuclear weapons.&#xD;
Pure fusion weapons would present far greater nuclear proliferation dangers since the acquisition of highly &#xD;
AND&#xD;
because of their smaller individual size and relative lack of fall-out.&#xD;
